description: Are you looking for a great collection of hilarious tones for your phone?  Freakin’ Funny Tones is the perfect application to tickle your funny bone!  There’s a bunch of unique ringtones to choose from in this FUN application. Several of these funny tones will be the perfect wake-up call and have you laughing in the morning. There are also tones featuring hilarious songs that will keep you entertained throughout the day. All of these Freakin’ Funny Tones and more, will put you in a fantastic mood everyday!   NOTE: We highly recommend that you have WiFi or good network connection in order to experience the full functionality of this app.
